0.3.0 cvs
=========
  * speed up kradio start
  * inet-stream-out plugin
  * use size_t instead of unsigned ints for all sizes!!! (was reason for
    problems in pointer arithmetic on amd64)
  * make file operations compliant with non-ascii-charsets (e.g. cyrillic)
  * tooltips in config dialog
  * option for display window type (entry in taskbar or toolbar window)
  * background pixmap for display
  * internet radio streams
  * translations
  * automatic station icon scaling
  * define final single/doubleclick tray icon behaviour
  * remote-kradio: run v4l plugin on remote machine, transfer data to
                   local machine
  * client-server concept: run kradio in background, make client gui individual
                           application

  * lirc config // done
  * title of main display with station name // done
  * .so-library plugins // done
  * plugin config // done
  * widgetplugin-show-button in radio view? // done
  * remove qlist.h // done
  * segfault fixes with 2.95.3 // done
  * fix recording problemes    // done
  * weekday selection for alarms // done
  * optimize recording data monitor: repaint only what is necessary // done
  * mp3 encoding with liblame_enc // done
  * time shift play (mp3, nogap, buffer=>mem or chained list of
    temp files) // done

  * if first run => less error messages, ask user for configuration,
    station scan, etc...
  * alsa support
  * RDS support
  * FAQ
      - devices (radio, mixer, dsp)
      -  mixer settings for recording
      - artsd
         
       
